      • refreshSuggestions

        void refreshSuggestions(AutocompleteTextField.AutocompleteModel<K> dataModel,
                        AutocompleteTextField<K> field)
        This may call model.setSuggestions(..). This is invoked after the contents of this text field change. This is executed on the EDT, so it needs to be relatively fast (or pass harder work off to another thread).
